---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Updates
permalink: /blog.html
description: "Diagnosis to surgery to recovery — documented honestly, with the chart and the truth side by side."
---

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 10rem 3rem 5rem; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-eyebrow { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem); line-height: 0.95; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-sub { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: var(--gray-light); max-width: 560px; }
  .surgery-banner { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04); border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12); padding: 1.5rem 3rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .surgery-banner-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--white); margin: 0 0 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .surgery-banner-link { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4); padding-bottom: 2px; }
  .surgery-banner-link:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
  .posts-grid { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 3rem 6rem; }
  .post-card { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 3rem 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
  .post-card:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
  .post-card:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
  .post-tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .post-card-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .post-excerpt { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gray-light); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px; }
  .post-arrow { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--gold); align-self: center; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .page-header, .posts-grid { padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; } .page-header { padding-top: 7rem; } .post-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .post-arrow { display: none; } .surgery-banner { gap: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; } }
</style>

<div class="page-header">
  <p class="page-eyebrow">From The Field</p>
  <h1 class="page-title">Walking Through This In Real Time.</h1>
  <p class="page-sub">From diagnosis to surgery to recovery. Documented honestly. The chart and the truth side by side.</p>
</div>

<div class="surgery-banner">
  <div style="width:100%;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem;">
    <p class="surgery-banner-title">Joe Made It Through Surgery. He's In Recovery.</p>
    <a href="/surgery-day.html" class="surgery-banner-link">Read: Surgery Day →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="posts-grid">
  {%- for post in collections.allPosts -%}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
    <div>
      <p class="post-tag">{{ post.data.date | postDate }} &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; {{ post.data.tag }} &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; {{ post.data.readTime }}</p>
      <h2 class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
    </div>
    <span class="post-arrow">→</span>
  </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
